dataIdInfo.idPurp: This data provides spatial representation of the watershed boundary, and geographic coordinates (UTM and decimal degrees) for identifying the centroid of the watershed boundary located at the Teller site west of Teller Road near mile marker 27.
dataIdInfo.idAbs: Watershed boundary was delineated in ArcGIS using the Hydrology Toolbox by Garrett Altmann, Lauren Charsley-Groffman, and Cathy Wilson. A 5m resolution IFSAR DEM was used to run the analysis.
dataIdInfo.idCredit: Lauren Charsley-Groffman, Garrett Altmann, and Cathy Wilson for creating watershed boundary.
